Name:Addition

Categories: Language

Syntax: 
`$Exp_1$ + $Exp_2$`

Types:

| `$Exp_1$`  |  `$Exp_2$` | `$Exp_1$ + $Exp_2$`  |
|:-----------|:-----------|:---------------------|
| `int`      |  `int`     | `int`                |
| `int`      |  `real`    | `real`               |
| `real`     |  `real`    | `real`               |


Description: Yields the numerical sum of the values of $Exp_1$ and $Exp_2$.

Examples:
<screen>
12 + 13
12 + 13.5
</screen>

